ging, not something less helpful.%0a%3c %0a%3c :Fact: When a goose gets sick or wounded or shot down, two geese drop out of formation to follow it down and protect it. They stay with the downed goose until it is either able to fly again or dies. Then they launch out on their own with another formation or catch up with their flock.%0a%3c :Lesson: If we have as much sense as geese, we will stand by one another.%0a%3c %0a
